message.body: Hey babe, how would you like to go for dessert and drinks when I get out?
No idea who will be open...
My phone died from all the navigating it did today. I'm about to hop in the shower. Let me know when you are getting out.
I just ate a bunch of desserts, but I still wouldn't mind a drink. I think we'll be done within the hour - hopefully I'll be able to give you an eta soon!
